  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Frontline Training for Border Guards and Police in Border Areas of Viet Nam</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In coordination with the Vietnamese National Border Guards (NBG), the project will support senior guard trainers to design and deliver an inter-agency training curriculum for frontline border guards and police officers to counter trafficking and migrant smuggling in border areas of Viet Nam. The inter-agency training curriculum will be designed in close cooperation with senior national police trainers from the Peoples Police Academy and the Border Guard Academy, including the Judicial Academy with the aim of institutionalizing the curriculum and capacity within existing police and border guard induction training programs.</narrative>
  </description>
